column2:
"...good work.
I think you did some really great
things."

"...I also gained from watching you
lead, and I was able to relax."

"...that's all for now. See you. I'll be
looking forward to having another
chance to work with you."

"……お疲れ様。
とてもいい動き、出来ていたと思う。"

"……私も、貴方がリードするのを見て
得るものがあったし、楽も出来た。"

"……それじゃ、私はこれで。
また機会があったら、よろしくね。"
